overview: Yeyet's love for Sapphire is only half-hearted, because Yeyet demands luxury from Sapphire who is only the son of a lute artist. When he meets the wealthy Angga, Yeyet immediately falls in love. Sapphire, who is heartbroken, accidentally meets Kinar, a rich man's son who is targeted by Angga. And love began to blossom.
title: Cinta Ada Karenamu
